Hello, my name is Nathan but I like to go by Nate. 

 I'm 29 years old and live in Federal Way, WA. I'm a Computer Science graduate from the University of Washington, Tacoma and am recently working my first professional job in this field as a technical project manager at TecAce Software Ltd. 

 When I am not working, I very much enjoy an active and healthy lifestyle through weight training and sports such as tennis and football. I like to go on walks, play with my dog, listen to music, watch anime, and hang out with close friends. Although I love being active, I am also very much a homebody and enjoy being a couch potato too.
